longBusinessSummary: Richards Packaging Income Fund, together with its subsidiaries, designs, manufactures, and distributes rigid packaging containers and related components in North America. It offers plastic, glass, and metal containers and closures. The company also offers packaging design and development, sourcing capabilities, and logistics management services. It serves food and beverage, healthcare, cosmetics, industrial, and pharmaceutical sectors. Richards Packaging Income Fund was founded in 1912 and is headquartered in Mississauga, Canada.
